snippet.title: Very Simple and Delicious Dessert Recipe – No Bake Dessert Idea
snippet.description:
This is Very Simple and Delicious Dessert Recipe you do not need long time to make at home! This No Bake Dessert Idea can help you to make your valentine day special. 
Ingredients & procedure
Take 2 tbsp rice flour and ¼ cup sugar
Blend ¼ cup peanut
Add 1 medium size banana and 300 ml milk
Blend them again
Mix the blended material with rice flour and sugar
Then boil it on medium flame for 5-6 minutes
After boiling, transfer it to dessert cup and let it cool completely
Keep it in refrigerator for 1 hour
Blend 1 cup strawberry 
Transfer it to pan
Add ¼ cup sugar
Boil it on medium flame for 6-7 minutes
Transfer it to dessert cup 
Keep it in refrigerator for 1 hour
Then serve the delicious dessert.

snippet.title: Lemon Delight - Lemon Jelly - Dessert Recipe
snippet.description:
Lemon Delight - Lemon Jelly - Dessert Recipe.
To make this lemon dessert or delight at first take some lemon peel from lemon as shown in video then take 1 tbsp lemon juice. After that take 1 cup sugar, 1/3 cup water, lemon peels and 1 tbsp lemon juice and boil them on medium flame for 6-8 minutes or until perfect consistency as shown in video. At this stage take 1/4 cup corn starch and 3/4 cup water. Then boil it for 3-4 minutes or until thick as shown in video. After that add sugar syrup and stir continuously for more 3-4 minutes. Boil more 5-6 minuets. At this stage you will get much thick mixture. Transfer it to a bowl and let it cool completely then keep it in refrigerator for at least 3 hours. After that coat the lemon delight dessert with desiccated coconut and serve.


© Hands Touch

snippet.title: PIZZA RECIPE WITHOUT YEAST IN PAN – NO MOZZARELLA CHEESE – EASY VEG PIZZA WITHOUT OVEN
snippet.description:
If you stay at home and need to make a pizza but you don’t have mozzarella cheese this pizza recipe is for you. To make this easy pizza you don’t need to buy any cheese from store. This veg pizza recipe without yeast and mozzarella cheese is very easy to make at home if you follow each and every step. 

Ingredients

For pizza sauce
1. Onion – 1 piece (small size)
2. Garlic – cloves
3. Ginger – 1 inch
4. Tomato – 1 piece (medium size)
5. Water – ½ cup
6. Oil – 1 tsp
7. Chopped garlic – ½ tsp
8. Mixed herb – ¼ tsp
9. Chili flakes – ¼ tsp
10. Red chili powder – ¼ tsp
11. Salt – as per taste


For Pizza toppings
1. Capsicum – ¼ cup
2. Tomato – ¼ cup
3. Onion – ¼ cup
4. Sweet corn – 2 tbsp
5. Oil – ½ tsp
6. Butter – ½ tsp
7. Salt – as per taste
8. Black pepper – ¼ tsp


For white sauce
1. Butter – 2 tbsp
2. All-purpose flour – 1 tbsp
3. Cold milk – ½ cup
4. Salt – as per taste


For cottage cheese
1. Milk – 1 cup
2. Vinegar – ½ tsp


For pizza dough
1. All-purpose flour – 1 cup
2. Baking powder – 1 tsp
3. Salt – ½ tsp
4. Curd/Yogurt – ¼ cup


Other ingredients
1. Mix herb
2. Black olive
3. Chili flakes

snippet.title: CHINGRI MALAIKARI RECIPE – PRAWN MALAI CURRY RECIPE – BENGALI SHRIMP CURRY
snippet.description:
Chingri malaikari recipe is one of the best Bengali shrimp curry recipe which is easy to make and delicious. This prawn malai curry recipe is very easy to make at home. In this chingri macher malaikari in bengali video I have shown you every step in easy way. Chingri macher recipe is also available in different restaurant. There are very few people who do not like chingri malai curry. Taste of chingri macher malaikari in bengali may be vary from place to place and cooking procedure. After watching the video, you will learn how to make chingri malai curry at home. This chingri macher malaikari in bengali is famous in Bangladesh, India and Pakistan. Not only above mentioned country but also famous to all over the world.  As yogurt is another ingredient of Bangladeshi chingri recipe, we can call it doi chingri recipe. Doi chingri is another delicious shrimp recipe in Indian subcontinent. By following this video you can learn how to cook doi chingri in easy way. I will suggest to follow every step of prawn recipe and serve to your dining table with plain rice or pulao. This Bengali shrimp curry is awesome and mouthwatering.

Ingredients:
Shrimp – 400 gram
Turmeric powder – 1 teaspoon
Salt – 1.5 teaspoon
Oil – 3 tablespoon
Bay leaf 2 pieces
Cloves – 3 pieces
Cardamom – 3 pieces
Cinnamon – 1 stick
Onion paste 1 cup
Ginger garlic paste – 1 tablespoon
Green chili paste – 1 teaspoon
Roasted cumin powder – 1 teaspoon
Roasted coriander powder – 1 teaspoon
Garam masala powder – 1 teaspoon
Yogurt – 3 tablespoon
Nut paste – 2 teaspoon
Coconut milk – 1.5 cup
Sugar – ½ teaspoon
Green chili – 4 pieces
Coriander leaves – a handful
Procedure of how to make chingri malai curry
1. At first add some oil in hot pan and fry each side of the shrimp for about 2 minutes on medium flame.
2. Keep some prawn fried oil aside
3. Add 1 cup onion paste and fry that for about 1 minute. After that add 1 tablespoon  ginger and garlic paste. Fry it for more 1 minute on medium flame
4. Now add 1 teaspoon cumin powder, 1 teaspoon turmeric powder, 1 teaspoon red chili powder and 1 teaspoon salt. Cook the mixture for 1 minute on medium flame.
5. Add 1.5 cup coconut milk.
6. In this step add fried chingri and cover the pan cook and it for 6-7 minutes on medium flame. 
7. Add 4 green chili and 1 handful of coriander leaves.
Your delicious item is ready, now you can serve it with hot plain rice or pulao.
